  "title": "Technician (Home Appliances)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Installation, Repair, and Maintenance:</strong> Carry out the installation, repair, and upkeep of various home appliances related to water, electricity, and gas systems.</li>\n  <li><strong>Technical Expertise:</strong> Apply hands-on experience and technical knowledge to diagnose and resolve issues in water, electrical, and gas systems effectively.</li>\n  <li><strong>Licensing Compliance: </strong>Possess valid licenses issued by the Energy Market Authority (EMA) and the Public Utilities Board (PUB) to perform work on electrical, gas, and water appliances.</li>\n  <li><strong>Customer Service:</strong> Engage with customers in a professional manner, attentively addressing their concerns and delivering practical solutions.</li>\n  <li><strong>Independent Operations:</strong> Work independently and proactively manage multiple service tasks, ensuring efficient and timely completion.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
